No. 09-10283. Junior Rojas, aka Ron John, aka Ron Joe, Petitioner v. United States. 560 U.S. 936, 130 S. Ct. 3339, 2010 U.S. LEXIS 4326.

176 L. Ed. 2d 1240,

May 24, 2010.

Petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.
